description: Bursting with flavour, this hoisin and garlic chicken stir-fry recipe is ready in just 15 minutes. Perfect for a speedy family midweek dinner.
keywords: Stir-fry,Low saturated fat,Tree nut free,Low sugar,Summer,Quick & easy dinner,High protein,High fibre,Rice,Chicken,Low fat
name: 15 Minute Hoisin & Garlic Chicken Stir-Fry Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 400g Cook traditional vegetables stir fry mix
90g Five Tastes Chinese hoisin & garlic stir fry shots

recipeInstructions.text: Heat rice according to packet instructions.
Heat 2 tbs vegetable oil in a large wok over medium-high heat. Stir-fry chicken, in 2 batches, for 4 minutes or until browned.
Add vegetable mix and stir-fry for 3 minutes or until vegetables start to soften.
Add stir-fry shots and 2 tbs water, then stir-fry for 1 minute or until chicken is cooked through. Divide rice and stir-fry among bowls, then serve.
